Interface ContiguousLexeme

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Lexeme
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiWordLexeme, WordLexeme

    public interface ContiguousLexeme
extends Lexeme
    An interface for contiguous lexical units. It is used just for consistency with SurfaceElement and ContiguousSurfaceElement classes.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
    See Also:
